3.00	Cameramen	Camera operator	A camera operator or cameraman is a professional operator of a film or video camera. In filmmaking, the leading cameraman is usually called a cinematographer, while a cameraman in a video production may be known as a television camera operator, video camera operator, or videographer, depending on the context and technology involved, usually operating a professional video camera.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2c/Ch10_Cameraman_filming_Vic_Lorusso%2C_Sydney%2C_NSW%2C_jjron%2C_01.12.2010.jpg/170px-Ch10_Cameraman_filming_Vic_Lorusso%2C_Sydney%2C_NSW%2C_jjron%2C_01.12.2010.jpg
